      "description": "We are proud to present an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle has been preserved in a state that mirrors its original showroom debut, characterized by a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains entirely unblemished. Meticulously maintained and held to the most exacting standards, this offering represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a vehicle of uncompromising quality. Its mechanical integrity and aesthetic presentation are, without exception, superlative.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
